---
import FAQItem from './FAQItem.astro';
---

<section class="bg-cream px-4 py-8 md:py-12">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="font-display text-red text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-wide mb-6 text-center">
      FAQ
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-cream-dark/50 rounded-lg px-4 md:px-6">
      <FAQItem question="HOW BIG ARE THE BUTTONS?">
        <p>1.25 inches. About the size of a quarter.</p>
      </FAQItem>

      <FAQItem question="HOW LONG DOES IT TAKE?">
        <p>Depends on the size of the order. Typically within 7 days.</p>
      </FAQItem>

      <FAQItem question="HOW MANY CAN I GET?">
        <p>As many as you need! Most orders are between 25-100 buttons, but I've done batches of 500+.</p>
      </FAQItem>

      <FAQItem question="WHAT DO I NEED TO PROVIDE?">
        <p>Just your graphic (PNG or vector preferred), a brief description of your organization, and how many buttons you need.</p>
      </FAQItem>

      <FAQItem question="DO YOU SHIP OUTSIDE NYC?">
        <p>I can, but I really love hand-delivering in NYC. If you're elsewhere, we can figure something out.</p>
      </FAQItem>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
